msgctxt "116_Rio"
msgid "Wow, this place has a great atmosphere. So calming."
msgstr "Wow, este lugar tiene una atmósfera única, muy relajante."

msgctxt "128_Player"
msgid "Heh. Yeah, I know what you mean."
msgstr "Je, si, sé a lo que te refieres."

msgctxt "140_Rio"
msgid "What are we waiting for? Let's go inside."
msgstr "¿A qué estamos esperando? Vamos dentro."

msgctxt "164_Rio"
msgid "Wow, this place has a great atmosphere. So calming."
msgstr "Wow, este lugar tiene una atmósfera única, muy relajante."

msgctxt "176_Player"
msgid "Um, wait a moment. I thought I had more cash than this..."
msgstr "Um, espera un momento. Pensé que iba con mas dinero encima..."

msgctxt "188_Rio"
msgid "Seriously? Not a single bill?"
msgstr "¿En serio? ¿Ni un solo billete?"

msgctxt "200_Player"
msgid "Yeah. Sorry..."
msgstr "Sí. Lo siento..."

msgctxt "212_Rio"
msgid "Oh. Um... That's... too bad. I should get going."
msgstr "Oh. Esto... Vaya, qué mal. Debería irme."

msgctxt "224_Player"
msgid "(I'd better remember to bring enough cash next time...)"
msgstr "(Será mejor que recuerde llevar suficiente dinero en efectivo la próxima vez...)"

msgctxt "332_Rio"
msgid "That was great. The food at Watami is excellent."
msgstr "Ha estado genial. La comida en Watami es de primera."

msgctxt "344_Player"
msgid "Glad you liked it."
msgstr "Me alegra que te haya gustado."

msgctxt "356_Rio"
msgid "Thank you so much for the meal!"
msgstr "¡Muchas gracias por la comida!"

msgctxt "368_Rio"
msgid "I had such a good time. I'll see you around, okay?"
msgstr "Me divertí mucho. Nos vemos, ¿vale?"

msgctxt "392_Rio"
msgid "Hmm. I could've eaten a bit more..."
msgstr "Mmm. Creo que me quedé con hambre..."

msgctxt "404_Player"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "416_Rio"
msgid "I had a great time. Come and see me at the club, okay?"
msgstr "Lo pasé de maravilla. Ven al club a verme, ¿vale?"

msgctxt "440_Rio"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "452_Player"
msgid "Something wrong?"
msgstr "¿Todo bien?"

msgctxt "464_Rio"
msgid "I'm sorry, just... I didn't really like what I had... That's all."
msgstr "Disculpa, es solo que... no me gustó mucho lo que pedí... Eso es todo."

msgctxt "476_Player"
msgid "Oh. Sorry about that."
msgstr "Oh. Lo siento mucho."

msgctxt "488_Rio"
msgid "I should be getting home. See you at the club."
msgstr "Debería regresar a casa. Nos vemos en el club."

msgctxt "500_Player"
msgid "(I shouldn't have ordered something she doesn't like...)"
msgstr "(No debería haber pedido algo que no le gusta...)"

